 course of this, will be exchanged\nperiodically in the phase difference of the JJ. The tunneling current in a\nmetal tip coupled to the JJ is shown to exhibit signs of the anyonic braiding\nphase of two MBSs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Nov 2019 17:47:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Jul 2020 13:49:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-10"}
