. Thus, we show that angular\nscattering in charge exchange collisions is important to include in analyses of\ninterstellar neutral atoms and pickup ions observed at 1 au and in the outer\nheliosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Nov 2019 19:44:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
